@UTF8
@Begin
@Languages:	eng
@Participants:	CHI Child, MOT Mother
@ID:	eng|corpus|CHI|4;0||||Child|||
@ID:	eng|corpus|MOT|||||Mother|||
@Comment:	%mor tier with clitics (tilde-separated: pos|stem~pos|stem),
	compound words on main tier (A+B), features with ampersand
@Comment:	Constructs: mor_post_clitic, mor_feature, compound words
*CHI:	it's a cookie .
%mor:	pron|it~aux|be&PRES det|a noun|cookie .
%gra:	1|4|SUBJ 2|1|AUX 3|4|DET 4|0|ROOT 5|4|PUNCT
*MOT:	he cannot do it .
%mor:	pron|he mod|can~neg|not verb|do pron|it .
%gra:	1|4|SUBJ 2|4|AUX 3|2|NEG 4|0|ROOT 5|4|OBJ 6|4|PUNCT
*CHI:	the teacup broke .
%mor:	det|the noun|teacup verb|break&PAST .
%gra:	1|2|DET 2|3|SUBJ 3|0|ROOT 4|3|PUNCT
*MOT:	there's a butterfly .
%mor:	pron|there~verb|be&3S det|a noun|butterfly .
%gra:	1|2|SUBJ 2|0|ROOT 3|4|DET 4|2|PRED 5|2|PUNCT
@End
